overview: Mixed Martial Archie & Colt Cabana face he Throwbacks in a “Loser Leaves CHIKARA” match! Gran Akuma’s trial series ends in a ladder match against Icarus while Hallowicked puts his mask on the line against the hair of Tim Donst! The Young Bucks fight F.I.S.T. for los Campeonatos de Parejas in the main event of CHIKARA’s second iPay Per View!
